thread.title: Liz C

author: Liz C
title: Liz C
text:
This is the third time I've used optimal print and it's simply excellent. The site is very easy to use and to navigate around the functions available, there's a great variety to choose from and the turnaround is overnight printing and shipped the next day (this may vary, but all three experiences have had overnight printing).
Would highly recommend for any occasion!
